- **Don't use `NavigationManager.Refresh(forceReload: true)` to propagate cascading value changes** â€” this destroys the circuit and forces a full page reload. Instead, inject `CascadingValueSource<T>` and call `NotifyChangedAsync(newValue)` to push updates to all `[CascadingParameter]` subscribers without a page reload.
